Author: oh-em-jizzles
Text: is she older or younger ? i can definitely relate

Author: bindingin
Text: Yes, and small things will get me! When I’m around my bf’s family (who are all skinny, obsessed with health, some ortho) I am often silenced- like I can’t get a word in and they don’t listen to me. I’m like okayyyy I guess my opinion will be more valuable when I’m skinny...   You’re the bigger person for starting conversations and listening to her. You are nice. Families are....forever difficult.
